                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020602-61-off328 t18020602-61-cd329"></join>, an iron shovel with a wooden handle, value 2s. and a dung fork, value 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18020602-61-victim481" type="victimName">
                  Samuel 
                  Ridge
               <interp inst="t18020602-61-victim481" type="surname" value="Ridge"></interp>
